These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Color: brown, apricot, white, orange
Nationality: malaysian, thai, turkish, american
1. Color:brown is on the right of Nationality:turkish##1
2. Nationality:american is on the far left##1
3. Nationality:turkish is between Nationality:thai and Color:apricot##2
4. Color:orange is on the far left##1
5. Color:white is between Color:apricot and Color:brown##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Color   | orange         | apricot   | white | brown       |
| Nationality      | american | malaysian | turkish   | thai |

