.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Sport: snowboarding, surfing, biathlon, lacrosse
Birthday: april, october, august, january
1. Birthday:january is between Sport:biathlon and Birthday:october##2
2. Sport:lacrosse is on the far right##1
3. Birthday:august is on the right of Birthday:april##1
4. Sport:snowboarding is on the left of Birthday:april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Sport         | surfing | snowboarding | biathlon | lacrosse |
| Birthday   | october    | january   | april | august       |

